   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Flavius Apollonios, strategos of the Arsinoite nome, Herakleides division. I, Gaius Iulius Nepotianus, veteran, landholder in Karanis, swear by the oath customary for the Romans, voluntarily and of my own free will, to be surety for the stay and appearance of Iulius Saturnilus, veteran, landholder in the same village, whom I shall produce . . .</ab>
